					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">SMB1 has fewer than 256 metatiles and fewer than 64 metatiles with each attribute value. This means it can use four metatile to hardware tile tables, one for each attribute value, each shorter than 256 bytes. (Source: Doppelganger's disassembly)</div>

